{"data":[{"id":563781628,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"55464481f151e029ac6799ab5e8812f5","url_token":"shou-xie-de-cong-qian-65-90","name":"手写的从前","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4b3466d496caa219ce172626f25d1d31_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4b3466d496caa219ce172626f25d1d31_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/55464481f151e029ac6799ab5e8812f5","user_type":"people","headline":"能用二元相图的绝不用三元，能泰勒展开的绝不用洛必达","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":257,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563781628","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276246,"updated_time":1546276246,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e他的证明说白了吧,“it is not only not right, it is not even wrong!”我想对他 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 说一下，不要沉迷在吃瓜群众的吹捧里，吃瓜群众永远是不嫌事大，想看热闹的，也有不少数学研究者奉劝过你了吧，现在回去抛弃杂念，好好学习，如果对这个问题感兴趣，等考上不错的大学了，你会学习更多的知识，从而增加你去攻破这个猜想的可能性!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你的证明，就像泡利当年，他的一位朋友给他看一位年轻物理学家的论文。那位朋友怀疑这篇论文没有太大的价值，但他还是想听听泡利的意见。泡利回复，这篇论文“连错都算不上”。这句话常被引用为“这不只不正确，甚至连错都算不上”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得，他开始很可能是中二病犯了，或者高考让他觉得非常难(他的知乎收藏夹都是一些什么数列的裂项相消之类的东西)，复习得也不怎么顺利，很枯燥，就有点想走捷径，希望通过一些其它的途径，迂回一下，绕过高考达到升学的目的!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是，他可能大大低估了哥德巴赫猜想的困难程度，他以为猜想形式上看上去很简单，不就是把一个大于2的偶数分解成两个质数之和吗，这还不好证明吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e同学，你要知道表述起来简单，不意味着证明起来也简单啊！能用初等工具就能攻破它，那历史上这么多数学家是吃干饭的吗？或者你认为你已经优秀到了连这些数学家都可以不放在眼里的程度了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最起码，你得懂一些最基本的解析数论，知道筛法这些东西吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得同学，做什么都得一步一步来，高考也好，研究哥德巴赫猜想也好，如果你是认真的，是对数论感兴趣，想去死磕哥德巴赫猜想的，不如先把下面这些论文读完再来谈证明?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eDeshouillers, J.-M.; Effinger, G.; te Riele, H. \u0026amp; Zinoviev, D. (1997). \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ams.org/era/1997-03-15/S1079-6762-97-00031-0/S1079-6762-97-00031-0.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\"A complete Vinogradov 3-primes theorem under the Riemann hypothesis\"\u003c/a\u003e (PDF). \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronic_Research_Announcements_of_the_American_Mathematical_Society\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eElectronic Research Announcements of the American Mathematical Society\u003c/a\u003e. \u003cb\u003e3\u003c/b\u003e (15): 99–104. \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003edoi\u003c/a\u003e:\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//doi.org/10.1090%252FS1079-6762-97-00031-0\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e10.1090/S1079-6762-97-00031-0\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apostolos_Doxiadis\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eDoxiadis, Apostolos\u003c/a\u003e (2001). \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uncle_Petros_and_Goldbach%27s_Conjecture\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eUncle Petros and Goldbach's Conjecture\u003c/a\u003e. New York: Bloomsbury. \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eISBN\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special%3ABookSources/1-58234-128-1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e1-58234-128-1\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMontgomery, H. L. \u0026amp; Vaughan, R. C. (1975). \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//matwbn.icm.edu.pl/ksiazki/aa/aa27/aa27126.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\"The exceptional set in Goldbach's problem\"\u003c/a\u003e (PDF). \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acta_Arithmetica\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eActa Arithmetica\u003c/a\u003e. \u003cb\u003e27\u003c/b\u003e: 353–370.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.i-programmer.info/news/112-theory/4211-goldbach-conjecture-closer-to-solved.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eTerence Tao proved that all odd numbers are at most the sum of five primes\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mathworld.wolfram.com/GoldbachConjecture.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eGoldbach Conjecture\u003c/a\u003e —at \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MathWorld\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eMathWorld\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michiel_Hazewinkel\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eHazewinkel, Michiel\u003c/a\u003e, ed. (2001) [1994], \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.encyclopediaofmath.org/index.php%3Ftitle%3Dp/g044550\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\"Goldbach problem\"\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Encyclopedia_of_Mathematics\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eEncyclopedia of Mathematics\u003c/a\u003e, Springer Science+Business Media B.V. / Kluwer Academic Publishers, \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eISBN\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special%3ABookSources/978-1-55608-010-4\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e978-1-55608-010-4\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.math.dartmouth.edu/%7Eeuler/correspondence/letters/OO0765.pdf\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eGoldbach's original letter to Euler — PDF format (in German and Latin)\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//primes.utm.edu/glossary/page.php%3Fsort%3DGoldbachConjecture\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eGoldbach's conjecture\u003c/a\u003e, part of Chris Caldwell's \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prime_Pages\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003ePrime Pages\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.ieeta.pt/%7Etos/goldbach.html\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eGoldbach conjecture verification\u003c/a\u003e, Tomás Oliveira e Silva's distributed computer search\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"他的证明说白了吧,“it is not only not right, it is not even wrong!”我想对他 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 说一下，不要沉迷在吃瓜群众的吹捧里，吃瓜群众永远是不嫌事大，想看热闹的，也有不少数学研究者奉劝过你了吧，现在回去抛弃杂念，好好学习，如果对这个问题感兴趣，…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=77\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=d